Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:04.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fscy120\blur4\3a&H4F\pos(232,652)}死之谷 Ⅲ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們是要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連這也不知道就跟過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你把我帶過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才沒有什麼目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是在尋找哈娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她這人出奇地不諳世事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她表情很豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總是盡情地嬉笑怒罵 還很能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們在一起有半年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而她突然間就失去了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被拋棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟正值十多年前那世界最混亂的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想必她現在已經比我年長多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那如果找到她了你打算怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果她需要我 我會伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果她已經找到別的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就在遠處看一下她然後離去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有可能她已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要找的東西還有一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}古今中外 不死者的願望都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在尋找死的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}死的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是很喜歡人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不要成為最後一個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後一個…人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對「最後一個人類」這句話多動點腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我想像 想像 想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後一個人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想抽到這張鬼牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這世上一個人也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有我一個人一直地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直…一直…一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是害怕成為世上最後一個人類是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你才想變成怪物是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發…發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該死 太失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是尤力先生您…救了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽好 不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之先穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要去修理那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙是救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欸？ 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你被踹下來之後 那裡就變成戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是誰做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是漢普尼所為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一旦發現要被襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他就會發動Suicide Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是自殺式攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他這人太離譜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過他助你脫險也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然看起來比較冷酷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但他不會無緣無故使用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論看起來多不合常理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他做事都有著他的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可不那麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過他也是在背負上不老不死的宿命後才變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即便這樣他以前和喜歡的女人在一起時還是挺正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的父親叫漢普尼韓伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他總有一天會來找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的是爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看情況應該沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對方有7個人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還特地用了鎮暴的橡膠彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}橡膠彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漢普尼就算死了也會按原來的模樣重生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要贏他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就要在不對他造成致命傷的情況下活捉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}換穿用的內褲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他自己肯定有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼說他也是有著不死之身的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是什麼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然為人很過份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但他意外地害怕寂寞且性情怪癖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們不去救他的話 他會變得更加彆扭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在他都真心認為自己是怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之 他不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會再這樣說他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫尤力·沙克馬·迪米特里耶維奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫艾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欸 你肯陪我一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他還稱我為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真巧啊 艾妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醒了嗎 漢普尼韓伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇怪了 我沒自報姓名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫希可 是你的忠實擁護者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說你在受到極度精神創傷的情況下死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像會失去那期間的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}混蛋 你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惡 記不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些傢伙對我做過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們這群混帳傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈哈 連髒話都煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惡 可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}認得這身裝扮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是在配合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}殺了你們 殺了你們 殺了你們 殺了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還是第一次想要成為某個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們到底是什麼人 有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但就算有辦法模仿你的外形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要模仿你那不老不死卻很難
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就變成了死人是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了抓住我這樣的笨蛋而出賣性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是不折不扣的大笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這份精神真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}默默無聞地制裁罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了灰色的正義而殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我對你的事情全都瞭若指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漢普尼韓伯特是想死對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想把自己那被神奪走的死給搶回來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就由我來殺死你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別誤會了 我的願望可不是死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說想死是騙人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你騙我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啊 你不可能騙我的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我從未把這些事告訴過任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過就特例告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是想單純地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是想幸福地死去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就如我一直所做的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也希望得到別人的看護
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.34,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住…住嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有朋友 妻子 孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有繼承者為我哭泣 為我惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留下些許的眷戀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.69,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}騙人的…騙人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想這樣離去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的願望就是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是如此平凡而無聊的死？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過已經沒有人能夠實現這願望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會…這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的願望是「幸福地活一輩子 然後幸福地死去」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要背叛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先成為我最重視的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事到如今卻要背叛我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天知道啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你單純是我們的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論多少次我都要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來啊 最後贏的肯定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位 幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是來埋葬你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}守墓者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 疤面小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們不是說好觀察好情況再衝進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們守墓者向來最重視速度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾 你來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然是為了來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是笨蛋嗎 跟我非親非故的人少管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是非親非故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說我跟你不是非親非故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我媽媽很漂亮卻又很孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}表情豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總是放聲大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生氣時會哭 飯量非常大 口哨吹得差
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不擅長做菜 很擅長打掃 措辭很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}討厭香煙和香水 異常喜歡吃甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她一直深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是艾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是名為漢普尼韓伯特的人類與名為阿爾法的守墓者的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}守墓者與人類的崽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漢普尼的女兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超高規格的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們好骯髒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 尤力先生和疤面小姐他們並不特別…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}死者所要前往的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}村裡的人都不想放棄這樣的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以…才會假裝活人讓年幼的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是我不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家其實早已經死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這話輪不到我來說 但希望你不要怨恨他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家…大家都是事出無奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很抱歉打斷你們的熱烈談話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拷問小艾的話漢普尼會高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是尤力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在做什麼 快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不逃 除非救出爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面小姐 麻煩你負責支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尋找戀人 沒想到卻遇上女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說起來哈娜那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然擅自失去蹤影 擅自生下孩子 擅自撒手歸西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我居然有女兒 太沒真實感了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是這塊料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我無法當一個好父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忘了嗎 我可是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 小孩子就是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好像還沒把我的名字告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這名字連你媽媽我都沒有告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的名字是奇茲納·亞斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你就叫艾·亞斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾·亞斯汀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不錯的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 爸爸 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明還有很多話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行了 好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失去了妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使女兒落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在朋友和守護者看護下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留下了眷戀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:49.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正小标宋_GBK\frz-90\pos(200,544)}食人玩具死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:49.72,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正小标宋_GBK\frz-90\fscx60\fscy60\pos(242,504)}漢普尼韓伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\blur5}然後爸爸以死人的身份再度睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\blur5}比誰都要深愛人類 都要痛恨死人的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\blur5}在唯一的一天裡輸給了自身的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\blur5}只為實現我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\blur5}只為給我留下回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\blur5}「爸爸 請你一直陪在我身邊」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\blur5}這句話是絕不能說出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生而為人 活以為人 卒以為人者 於此長眠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今後有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是守墓者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我要成為守墓者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果神要捨棄世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我就要拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:31.59,Next,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.10,Next,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7}這裡這個少年怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.68,Next,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}性質惡劣的迷幻藥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.81,Next,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7}是守墓者和人類的混血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:38.93,Next,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an9}感覺得出有還沒埋葬的死人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:40.81,Next,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是死的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:43.40,Next,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an2}雖然明白了 但是不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:44.06,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\fscy120\blur4\3a&H4F\an5\pos(640,440)}歐塔斯 Ⅰ
